Script,Misfit
setDealerCode(`

dealer south
produce 1000

### Import 'canned' code for Leveling, Calm Opponents, and Predict Opening Bid 
Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/-Script-Leveling
Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/-Script-Calm-Opponents
Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/-Script-Predict-Opening-1-Bid

nS = oneSpade   and spades(north)<2
nH = oneHeart   and hearts(north)>2
nD = oneDiamond and diamonds(north)<2
nC = oneClub    and clubs(north)<2

sOpens = (oneSpade or oneHeart or oneDiamond or oneClub) and (nS or nH or nD or nC) and hcp(south)>11
nMin = hcp(north)>5  and hcp(north)<11
nMid = hcp(north)>10 and hcp(north)<13
nMax = hcp(north)>12

# Level the deal
lMin = nMin and keep
lMid = nMid and keep
lMax = nMax and keep

levelTheDeal = (lMin and lMid and lMax)

sOpens and (nMin or nMid or nMax) and calmOpps
and levelTheDeal

action
average "Min" 100 * nMin
average "Mid" 100 * nMid
average "Max" 100 * nMax


`,"E",true)
Script
Button,Misfit,\n\
--- South opens and North has a misfit with various strengths.\n\
  • 6-10\n\
  • 11-12\n\
  • 13+\n\
%Misfit%
